name: 1 Minute Sea-Monkeys
description:
Big Bro is out of the house for 1 minute to buy an onion. He gave you the intense responsibility of keeping his sea-monkeys alive while he's gone! Click the correct buttons at the correct time to keep his valuable collection allive.

This game was made in 3 hours for trijam 96.

Music: https://opengameart.org/content/green-hills-0
